    <refsection id="Description_CMRC_IdealDifferential">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            This block is a model of an ideal differential gear without inertia. The angular velocities are computed
            with the fundamental relationship:
        </para>
        <para>
            <latex>
                \begin{eqnarray}
                \Large{\omega_{drive shaft/0}} = ratio * \frac{\Large{\omega_{right wheel/0} + \omega_{left wheel/0}}}{2}
                \end{eqnarray}
            </latex>
        </para>
    </refsection>
